{"tid":2061149,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[消失的新聞］由聽日起12.6.2019 嘅新聞就會喺 RTHK 嘅網頁消失","createTime":"2020-06-12T07:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T08:06:28.000Z","uid":185251,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb7e779d2286f4e2f8cf7efaaffda47dc5e7383","tid":2061149,"uid":185251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5LtdeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5LtdeV.jpg&h=fa45862e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廢話唔多講，大家都知過去一年嘅新聞對將來編寫香港歷史有幾咁重要，能夠以中立角度報導事實嘅媒體更加係寥寥可數。香港電台作為公營機構，喺資源緊絀嘅情況下，仍然盡心盡力為香港人服務。但剛剛上去港台網頁就發現&rsquo;新聞重溫&lsquo; 只可以睇返最近一年嘅新聞。而家仲可以睇到舊年612 嘅新聞，但之前嘅已經睇唔返，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">換言之，聽日就唔可以再喺港台網頁重溫612嘅報導</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道嗰啲新聞已經消失喺呢個世上，定只係佢哋archive 咗無公開。如果係消失咗固然唔能夠接受，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但若果係後者，將來中共接收港台時，1984情節就會隨時發生，改寫歷史無難度。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個post 唔係要攻擊港台，只係想推比多啲人知道，睇吓有無其他媒體或者議員跟進，又或者有無IT 巴絲可以喺事情解決之前有辦法backup啲報導。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lsquo;Who controls the past controls the future. Who controls the present controls the past.&lsquo; &mdash; 1984 by George Orwell</span></span></em>"},{"pid":"e6cbf15c61205e1744561193395960925999988e","tid":2061149,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"可以用Internet Archive去睇"},{"pid":"f343c2f3529cbfee80bae7dff423f114ab2d52b9","tid":2061149,"uid":122402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Back Up!!!</span></strong>"},{"pid":"535950032d43fffd61d0306477a1c87e5191e804","tid":2061149,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6cbf15c61205e1744561193395960925999988e","tid":2061149,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":